foundry-core (1.0.1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Drop ubuntu-base deps (bash-completion, man-db, sudo, libvte-2.91-0)
    — these are pre-installed on every Ubuntu system and have no place
    in a developer toolkit metapackage targeting existing installs.

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 +0700

foundry-core (1.0.0) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Splits desktop-agnostic developer tools out of
    foundry-anvil so existing Ubuntu (non-KDE) users can install the
    full toolkit without pulling in KDE/Plasma/Kirigami dependencies.
    See docs/plans/2026-05-28-foundry-core-desktop-split.md.

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Wed, 28 May 2026 00:00:00 +0700
